tv commercials portraying what it feels like to chew  gum perez led the efforts of improving slimmer packaging slim pack with flavor improvements across both extra and wrigley brands – dushan duke petrovichedit dushan petrovich – succeeded perez almost immediately after mars incorporateds  purchase of wrigley in  wrigleys global innovation center received the leed gold certification through wrigleys commitment to global sustainability in the  olympic games in vancouver british columbia wrigley was the official confectionery supplier of the games in which the company sported olympicthemed packs and products –present martin radvanedit martin radvan became the president of the wrigley company after petrovich he is responsible for the company’s worldwide strategy operations and business performance subsidiariesedit the wrigley company limited amurol confections company northwestern flavors llc changes in gumedit in some countries xylitol is used to sweeten gum instead of aspartame by avoiding sugar the chance of tooth decay is lowered since the sugar otherwise used may turn into acid after chewing the gum it is also claimed that in chewing it may help to remove food residues xylitolbased products are allowed by the us food and drug administration to make the medical claim that they do not promote dental cavities new productedit wrigley temporarily halted production and sales of its new alert energy gum as the food and drug administration investigates the safety of caffeinatedfood products brandsedit gumedit united states a newspaper ad from  for three types of wrigleys gum juicy fruit  spearmint  doublemint  freedent  big red  extra  winterfresh  hubba bubba orbit reintroduced  orbit white eclipse    canada  doublemint excel excel mist excel white extra extra professional extra professional white hubba bubba juicy fruit freedent the wrigley company ltd estover plymouth uk airwaves hubba bubba doublemint extra altoids juicy fruit tunes wrigleys spearmint lockets skittles